{"tid":264232,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"又要言華夏文化數千年，又要言孔孟一脈相承才稱華夏，結果自相矛盾矣。","createTime":"2017-05-30T15:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T17:17:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"532440a4aaa26c597500214858a4943e121e8ab6","tid":264232,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1676794835956347/photos/a.1698503017118862.1073741828.1676794835956347/1699158143720016/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1676794835956347%2Fphotos%2Fa.1698503017118862.1073741828.1676794835956347%2F1699158143720016%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=VcvqahbBom5WgVZjvfVCpDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f5437c78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1676794835956347/photos/a.1698503017118862.1073741828.1676794835956347/1699158143720016/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/18699909_1699158143720016_7929214603729625748_n.jpg?oh=7b04fa929fa3265f9bbf7be97ed81b09&amp;oe=599E7370\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F18699909_1699158143720016_7929214603729625748_n.jpg%3Foh%3D7b04fa929fa3265f9bbf7be97ed81b09%26oe%3D599E7370&h=f9dc8583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對華夏認知不足的結果。又要言華夏文化數千年，又要言孔孟一脈相承才稱華夏，結果自相矛盾矣。<br />\n<br />\n孔孟一脈相承乃宋國張橫渠、程明道、程伊川所倡，此前沒有此論。若華夏必然等於孔孟一脈相承，那麼宋國之前就沒有華夏，華夏就沒有數千年呢。<br />\n又要言華夏，又對華夏認知不足，正是莊元生之流矣。<br />\n<br />\nLewis Loud"},{"pid":"aefbffe06d975aeb86b9ae3755aef628d2a25b14","tid":264232,"uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"青城派傻佬只有佢地係華夏一脈相傳，任何人不得挑戰權威，同冷血合組邪教洗班盲毛腦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3c8675796e9e8e7dfbcf43bfa0c801c73972f2","tid":264232,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青城派傻佬只有佢地係華夏一脈相傳，任何人不得挑戰權